# agents/memory/.project.example
# Template for the runtime project name file. The agent that bootstraps
# the project copies this to agents/memory/.project (no extension, at the
# top of the module) and replaces the value with the actual project
# slug (the Neo4j group_id).
#
#   cp agents/memory/.project.example agents/memory/.project
#   # edit agents/memory/.project and replace the value below
#
# Rules for the project slug:
#   - Lowercase, no spaces, ASCII letters/digits/underscore/hyphen only.
#   - Must match the Neo4j group_id used by every write in this checkout.
#   - Re-running the seed is idempotent within a slug; switching slugs
#     creates a fresh, isolated graph.

malariasentinel
